{"tid":2001980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：立法會內會恢復運作後 《國歌法》即上大會二讀","createTime":"2020-05-05T02:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T02:54:55.000Z","uid":144018,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a10d4d297bf5f00d12b4df0eb62845fb856d2824","tid":2001980,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:40:44.000Z","msg":"關於哪些法案屬內會需急切處理的議案，是否包括《國歌法》。林鄭月娥指《國歌法》已完成法案委員會審議，報告亦已提交內會，目前「只爭埋門一腳」，即與內會主席商討何時恢復二讀。她期望立法會大會通過財政預算案後，便可以恢復《國歌法》二讀，又借機諷郭榮鏗指這才是立法會正常的程序。她又表示有人對外聘法律意見「唔岩心水」便大加批評，而政府與該意見只是「咁岩一致」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇字都諗到777個衰樣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073092&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1kcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=ffb21956\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073092&h=78e29940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073092</a>"},{"pid":"019e2cfc0b759d9890d1840425e320670e818fb1","tid":2001980,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:41:57.000Z","msg":"預左過硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國做野未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aecd07f3583e610b2ea80958ce6b5693d51f1c4f","tid":2001980,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/